---

<section id="reviews" class="py-20 bg-off-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray mb-4">
        What Our Customers Say
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Don't just take our word for it — hear from businesses we serve across the Triangle.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-muted/10 relative">
        <div class="text-primary/15 absolute top-4 right-6">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10H14.017zM0 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151C7.546 6.068 5.983 8.789 5.983 11H10v10H0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <!-- Stars -->
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "Smart Vend NC transformed our break room. Our team actually gets excited about the snack selection now, and I love that the machine is always stocked. The AI technology is impressive — it knows what we want before we do!"
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-muted/15 pt-4">
          <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-gray">Jennifer Walsh</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-muted">Office Installation &middot; October 2024</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-muted/10 relative">
        <div class="text-primary/15 absolute top-4 right-6">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10H14.017zM0 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151C7.546 6.068 5.983 8.789 5.983 11H10v10H0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "As a facilities manager, I've dealt with vending companies for 20 years. Smart Vend NC is different. Zero hassle, always responsive, and the healthy options make our wellness committee happy. Best decision I've made."
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-muted/15 pt-4">
          <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-gray">Robert Martinez</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-muted">Corporate Campus &middot; August 2024</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-muted/10 relative">
        <div class="text-primary/15 absolute top-4 right-6">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10H14.017zM0 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151C7.546 6.068 5.983 8.789 5.983 11H10v10H0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "We run a 24-hour gym and needed vending that matched our brand. Smart Vend NC delivered custom-wrapped machines with exactly the products our members want. The cashless system is seamless."
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-muted/15 pt-4">
          <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-gray">Amanda Foster</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-muted">Fitness Center &middot; September 2024</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
